Package: RabbitR
Type: Package
Title: User fiendly linear mixed model analysis solved with Bayesian
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Marina", "Martinez-Alvaro", email = "mamaral9@upv.es",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <mamaral9@upv.es>
Description: This is a teaching-oriented package for linear mixed models solved using Bayesian theory.
